{"tid":926834,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"有冇人用StreetVoice聽歌","createTime":"2018-12-03T17:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T13:50:40.000Z","uid":201975,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"49e7bcc83b3e3a0d9396fabdd8dceac94488256f","tid":926834,"uid":201975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"因為用呢個app而識多咗好多台灣、北京、內地既獨立音樂人同樂隊，成日都會無意中發掘到新野，耳仔keep住聽到新鮮野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排我自己好鐘意就有呢啲:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">十一種孤獨 宿陽羽</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u6SrA6p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu6SrA6p.png&h=8cdb7484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">直覺的莽撞 中華路樂隊</span><br />\n好鐘意好鐘意主唱既唱腔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iDcZV64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiDcZV64.png&h=5ae71e1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">愛情雨 9m88</span><br />\n可能有聽開佢既都唔陌生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢呢首真係由cover到節奏音質歌詞都好有年代feel<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YoTqRHH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYoTqRHH.png&h=aaff4502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實都係想大家互相交流下平時聽開啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想再聽多啲新曲風，識多啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0c216cb1b756d4486909ef446ee19badba4949","tid":926834,"uid":149630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:49:27.000Z","msg":"謝春花<br />\n只道尋常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6514f62d12d058a43e8c4464258b6dc2c170cfa","tid":926834,"uid":201975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb0c216cb1b756d4486909ef446ee19badba4949","t